<p>请查看完整邮件内容...</p>
</div>

<div class="section-card" style="background: #faf5ff; border-left: 4px solid #a855f7;">
<div class="section-header"><span class="section-icon">📈</span><h2>趋势分析</h2></div>
<p>请查看完整邮件内容...</p>
